<subSubSection pageId="6" pageNumber="571" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="6.[151,1437,153,503]" pageId="6" pageNumber="571">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,353,188,215]" pageId="6" pageNumber="571">Distribution.</emphasis>
Currently this species is only known from its 
<typeStatus box="[884,932,189,215]" pageId="6" pageNumber="571">type</typeStatus>
locality, Mt. Ailao in South Central 
<collectingRegion country="China" name="Yunnan" pageId="6" pageNumber="571">Yunnan Province</collectingRegion>
, Southwestern 
<collectingCountry box="[424,491,225,251]" name="China" pageId="6" pageNumber="571">China</collectingCountry>
