<figureCitation box="[506,590,225,252]" captionStart="FIGURES 16" captionStartId="7.[151,264,1236,1261]" captionTargetBox="[151,1435,291,1217]" captionTargetId="figure@7.[151,1435,291,1217]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURES 16. Distribution map of S. liuzihaoi sp. nov. and its related species. Records of distribution are taken from Huang (2003), Xue et al. (2015) and the present study." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3662026" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3662026/files/figure.png" pageId="6" pageNumber="571">Fig. 16</figureCitation>
